  <title>WebKit2.Settings.enable_frame_flattening</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
Settings.enable_frame_flattening: Boolean (Read / Write / Construct)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Whether to enable the frame flattening. With this setting each subframe is expanded
to its contents, which will flatten all the frames to become one scrollable page.
On touch devices scrollable subframes on a page can result in a confusing user experience.</p>

